{"tid":972201,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國外交部：美艦擅闖西沙群島領海　中方向美方嚴正交涉","createTime":"2019-01-07T08:26:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-08T01:07:08.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"d79cb666ed4e22d232118dcdeabd4f66c32c4403","tid":972201,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T08:26:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1436845_1_20190107162320.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1436845_1_20190107162320.jpg&h=d3a09c1a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在北京，外交部表示，美國海軍軍艦未經中方允許，擅自進入中國西沙群島領海，中方於是派出軍艦軍機，依法對美艦實施查證識別與警告驅離，中方亦已就此向美方提出嚴正交涉。 <br />\n<br />\n外交部發言人陸慷表示，美艦有關行為違反中國法律及相關國際法，侵犯中國主權，中方堅決反對，敦促美方立即停止此類挑釁行動。<br />\n<br />\n對於事件對中美當前開展的經貿磋商的影響，陸慷表示，妥善解決好中美之間存在的各種問題，包括經貿問題，對兩國及世界有利，雙方都有責任營造必要的良好氣氛。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1436845-20190107.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1436845-20190107.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=MmsljSwmbRLmMNnuRoW8HwRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=5b63cd8d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1436845-20190107.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=8b4eae1f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1436845-20190107.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"2c994bacb6ff7f6182df21f7d22af3e59c90227b","tid":972201,"uid":51057,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T08:31:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/01/233235_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F01%2F233235_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg&h=5a77176e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cf07b0325c2fb52a5f54c223